OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mainly dry and cloudy day
OL,6,Fwith just the odd shower, although
OL,7,Fthese may become more widespread in
OL,8,Fthe west later. Some occasional
OL,9,Fbrightness in the southeast. Breezy at
OL,10,Ftimes.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FIt will be cloudy and mostly
OL,13,Fdry through the evening and overnight.
OL,14,FA few outbreaks of rain possible
OL,15,Fhowever, with these mainly in the
OL,16,Fwest. Winds easing.
OL,17,
OL,18,CSunday:FAnother cloudy and mostly dry
OL,19,Fday with a few spells of light rain
OL,20,Fpossible in the north and west. Some
OL,21,Foccasional bright spells in the east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
