OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMostly
OL,6,Fdry and cloudy Monday and Tuesday with
OL,7,Fa few outbreaks of rain in the north
OL,8,Fand west and some brightness in the
OL,9,Fsoutheast. Dry Wednesday with bright
OL,10,Fspells developing.
